1
00:00:21,843 --> 00:00:25,886
[SPEAKER_00]: Hello, everyone, and welcome to your show, Medford Happenings.

2
00:00:26,867 --> 00:00:33,773
[SPEAKER_00]: I am John Petrella, and I am here to introduce you to a show that is for and about the city of Medford.

3
00:00:34,553 --> 00:00:42,020
[SPEAKER_00]: The show is being produced by people like me who believe that there is a need for regular sharing of local information.

4
00:00:43,100 --> 00:00:50,807
[SPEAKER_00]: Our program will discuss our community, the people, neighbors, events and happenings around Medford.

5
00:00:52,448 --> 00:00:56,711
[SPEAKER_00]: We'll look into Method's past, its present, and the future.

6
00:00:58,152 --> 00:01:12,542
[SPEAKER_00]: Our topics of discussion will include local politics and government, business and commerce, the arts and culture, senior issues and concerns, our many sports teams and recreation.

7
00:01:13,243 --> 00:01:18,967
[SPEAKER_00]: We'll also touch on philanthropy and charity, public safety and wellness,

8
00:01:19,963 --> 00:01:23,745
[SPEAKER_00]: Things to see, places to go, and who's who in Medford.

9
00:01:25,165 --> 00:01:27,066
[SPEAKER_00]: We have some great shows planned.

10
00:01:27,826 --> 00:01:36,710
[SPEAKER_00]: Look for us on Medford Community Network website, mcn02155.com.

11
00:01:37,451 --> 00:01:42,533
[SPEAKER_00]: We look forward to hearing from you and see you next time on Medford Happenings.

